profile: With professional, dedicated plumbing service to all major cities and surrounding areas in Alberta, and with some of the best plumbers in the industry, The Gentlemen Plumbers work hard to exceed your expectations and deliver quality. If you need a plumber, call us today for plumbing or heating issues, leaky sinks and faucets, clogged drains, toilet, bathtub and shower repairs, furnace cleaning and repairs, hot water tanks and tankless hot water heaters, furnace installation and maintenance, trenchless pipe repair, camera sewer inspection, and more! We have local branches in Calgary, Edmonton, Red Deer, Lethbridge, and Medicine Hat, with extended service all over Southern Alberta, including Camrose, Sherwood Park, St. Albert, Airdrie, High River, Crossfield, Carstairs, Olds, Innisfail, Wetaskiwin, Leduc, Lacombe, Okotoks, Nanton, Taber, Cardston, Didsbury, Brooks, Crowsnest Pass, Cochrane, Strathmore, Sundre, Three Hills, Ponoka, Fort Macleod, Pincher Creek, Bowden, Fort Saskatchewan, Chestermere, Sylvan Lake, Spruce Grove, and Stony Plain.

Furnace Fellas is your trusted brand when you need any Furnace or Plumbing repairs.  We are always looking for ways to help improve our brand experience. We live by our core values. "honesty, passion, teamwork, purpose"  we as a team look forward to servicing your home or business and making sure that we give the best possible service, industry leading warranties and fully trained staff from the first phone call to the final walk through.

Furnace Fellas is a leader in the service industry, we guarantee when our team services your home comfort system we will make it the best it can be with our full time service department we make sure that you are fully aware of any possible problems with our full comprehensive inspection.

Furnace Fellas wants you to know that we care. We will be able to work with you through any problems that you may have with your heating and cooling systems.

profile: Nova is committed to providing HVAC service with the highest integrity. Based in Airdrie, we serve clients throughout Calgary and surrounding areas. Nova was founded on the belief that HVAC companies should treat each customer the way we’d like our own families to be treated. Owned and operated by Chad McMonagle, Nova’s ambition is to become a trusted advisor to each client. To earn that trust, Nova openly presents all possible options, and, if the client chooses to hire them, performs work to the highest standard.

profile:
Here at Highcliffe Mechanical we are committed in providing competitive pricing with unparalleled service. We provide Residential and Commercial Plumbing, Heating, Gasfitting and Air Conditioning service to Calgary, Airdrie, Chestermere, Cochrane, Okotoks and multiple surrounding areas. 
From a leaky faucet, clogged drain, no heat or hot water, renovations, retro-fits, new installs through to new builds our dedicated team of professionals are here for you. With our 24/7 emergency service you can count on Highcliffe. Don't hesitate to call or message, we are here to help!
products: Sinks, faucets/taps, tubs, showers, toilets, bidets, fixtures, urinals, furnaces, thermostats, humidifiers, boilers, hot water tanks, instantaneous tankless water heaters, garage unit heaters, radiant heaters, water softeners, water filtration, pumps, fire places, UV lamps, A/C units, air purifiers.
services: Residential and Commercial Plumbing, Heating, Gasfitting and Air Conditioning. New installs, service, repairs, drain cleaning, renovations, retro-fits, new builds, preventative maintenance and lease bays.

licenses: Red Seal Endorsed, Master Plumber, Gasfitter (B)
memberships: Better Business Bureau (BBB), Energy Efficiency Alberta, Renovation Find

profile:
Airdrie Air Ltd was formed in 2002. We are active members of the Better Business Bureau (with a top-rating of A+), 5 star customer ratings and members of the Airdrie Chamber of Commerce.

Airdrie Air services include; Heating, Ventilation, Air Conditioning and Controls for Airdrie, Crossfield and Rocky view. We provide maintenance service contracts which can be cancelled anytime without any penalties or lock-ins. If there is a problem with your system, we can diagnose it and then let you know up front the price of repair so you have no surprise billings or hidden costs.

High prices for utilities are growing every day. Airdrie Air Ltd can help you keep your heating and air conditioning costs down by maintaining your equipment to run at its peak performance. We pride ourselves in superior quality service so your work or home can be comfortable and safe.

Airdrie Air Ltd realizes that in order for a company to be successful, customer service, quality workmanship and superior products must always be there for you, guaranteed.
